        <Param val="True" valType="bool" updates="None" name="syncScreenRefresh"/>
        <Param val="In this item-scene association task, you will see different items (objects or animals) placed in one of the jungle or undersea scenes you memorized previously. After each presentation of an item and a scene, you will be asked to report whether they are related or unrelated. &amp;#10;&amp;#10;An item is related to a scene if you think it is plausible that such an item would live or would be used in such a scene in real life. If not, they are unrelated.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will see each item-scene pair three times in total.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Press SPACEBAR to continue." valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
